headline: Booking named Best Idea for 2025 at TD Cowen
summary: Investing.com -- TD Cowen analysts named Booking Holdings (NASDAQ:BKNG) as their best stock idea for 2025, citing a continued runway for share gains and a new cost-efficiency plan.

headline: Agoda Highlights Bangkok, Singapore, and Seoul as 2024's Top Flight Destinations
summary: Digital travel platform Agoda unveils its list of the top five international flight destinations of 2024. It's Thailand's capital city Bangkok where most Agoda-booked flights touched down this year.
